ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on HR Analytics for a multinational company (MNC) using Python. The goal is to analyze employee data to uncover insights related to employee status, work modes, department distribution, attrition, and workforce trends. The analysis helps HR teams and management make data-driven decisions regarding employee retention, workforce planning, and organizational performance.

The project is implemented in a Jupyter Notebook and follows a structured, question-driven analytical approach.

